6,http://www.armslist.com/posts/3699006,For Sale:  Model 12 - TRENCH GUN - Winchester,"Shawnee, Oklahoma City, Oklahoma","$ 3,500","Listed On: Tuesday, February 10, 2015",Shotguns,Winchester                                                                                ,12 Gauge                                                                                ,Pump Action                                                                                ,Shotgun,"I am considering letting go of my authentic, 1942 Model 12 Trench Gun. It is serial number correct with all the proper markings. This gun has not been re-armored and was used in the Pacific theater. This gun has a lot of personality. The fore grip has some awesome trench art scribed into it. (see pics). The only flaw with the gun is the correct stock has a butt pad added. The gun functions like the pro it is... Very smooth and not sloppy at all. The bore is smooth and clean. And yes... It will slam fire as fast as you can pump it. If you are interested in a real piece of WWII history - touch base and make an offer. I will ship only to FFL.  Buyer pays for shipping fee and insurance.  405 609-70sevenseven"
